      "answer": "D",
      "sourceFileId": "社工師:112110:c103:s0304:Q",
      "answerSourceFileId": "社工師:112110:c103:s0304:S",
      "manualPatch": false
    },
    {
      "id": "社工師:112110:c103:s0304:q02",
      "number": 2,
      "stem": "需求是社會政策重要的概念，高夫（Ian Gough）將需求分類為基本需求（basic needs）與中介需 求（intermediate needs），下列敘述何者錯誤？",
